@startuml UC-105_Activity
title UC-105: Onboard Partner (Activity)

|Integration Manager|
start
:Login to SCP;
:Create Integration Partner Record;
:Define API Access Scopes (Read/Write/Notify);

|Tenant Admin|
:Review Partner Agreement & Security Scope;
if (Aligned with Policy?) then (yes)
  :Approve & Activate Integration;
else (no)
  :Reject / Request Scope Reduction;
  stop
endif

|SCP Core: Security|
:Generate ClientID & Secret;
:Register Webhook URL;

|Partner Tech Lead|
:Receive Credentials (via Secure Channel);
:Initiate Connectivity Test (Ping);

|SCP Core: Integrations|
:Validate API Key & Hash;
if (Valid?) then (yes)
  :Respond 200 OK / Authenticated;
  :Mark Integration as HEALTHY;
else (no)
  :Respond 401 Unauthorized;
  :Log Security Event;
endif

stop
@enduml
